episodes.description:
DO YOU LIKE GAMES? is a comedy podcast that bodes the question: do you like games? Do you? Do we? Tune in as Trog, Baaulp, Log, and Wayne, go over some wet ‘n’ spicy leaks from next week’s E3 expo. Are you pumped for Balloon Race’s return? Will you mourn Donald Duck’s death? Will Yoshi become real? 
Do you like games? For our second episode, we decided to go over some juicy leaks from our boy Edward over at E3. While we’ve honed the formula a bit more with this one, we’re still working on the technical side of things, so we are aware of the audio issues! If you enjoyed this, please tell your friends! Lend us your energy!

episodes.description:
DO YOU LIKE GAMES? is a comedy podcast that bodes the question: do you like games? Do you? Do we? Tune in as Trog, Baaulp, Log, Scorpy, and Wayne, review new hit titles and rediscover old classics. Why did Kratos kill his son? Why did Nintendo ruin Funky Kong? What’s a PSP? Do you like games?
This is our pilot episode: we recorded this a few weeks ago to play around with the idea and found that this is a hell of a good time to record. We’re aware of the audio issues and hope to improve on them in the future: but we need to get this out there! If you enjoyed this, please tell your friends! Lend us your energy!
